'''Murgs''' were creatures from the planet [[Terephon]] inside the [[Hapes Consortium/Legends|Hapes Consortium]]. They were as long as [[Speeder bike/Legends|speeder bikes]], had stubby legs, and flipper-shaped feet. They were gray, slimy, and tubular. They were used as hunting animals.

